sequenceDiagram
    participant User as CLI User
    participant CLI as kubectl-odh<br/>(local process)
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant FS as Local Filesystem
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant GH as GitHub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over User,K8s: Flow 1: Upgrade Readiness Assessment (lint)
        User->>CLI: kubectl odh lint --target 3.5<br/>(stdin / flags)
        CLI->>K8s: GET DataScienceCluster (v2, fallback v1)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: DSC spec + status
        CLI->>K8s: GET DSCInitialization<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: DSCI (namespaces, version)
        CLI->>K8s: GET CRDs, Subscriptions, CSVs<br/>PackageManifests, Workloads
        K8s-->>CLI: Platform + workload state
        Note over CLI: Execute 38 checks<br/>dependency → service → platform →<br/>component → workload ordering
        Note over CLI: Classify: Prohibited > Blocking ><br/>Advisory > None
        CLI-->>User: Structured report (stdout)<br/>Exit: 0=pass, 1=advisory, 2=blocked
    end

    rect rgb(252, 228, 236)
        Note over User,FS: Flow 2: Migration Execution (migrate run)
        User->>CLI: kubectl odh migrate run kserve.serverless-to-raw<br/>(stdin / flags / --dry-run)
        CLI->>K8s: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>Pre-validate RBAC permissions
        K8s-->>CLI: Allowed / Denied
        alt RBAC Denied
            CLI-->>User: Error: insufficient permissions<br/>(lists missing permissions)
        end
        CLI->>K8s: GET current state<br/>(InferenceServices, ServingRuntimes, etc.)
        K8s-->>CLI: Current resource state
        CLI->>FS: Write backup files<br/>(pre-migration state)
        Note over CLI: Execute action<br/>Prepare → Run lifecycle<br/>Hierarchical step recording
        CLI->>K8s: PATCH/CREATE resources<br/>(deployment mode, annotations, etc.)
        K8s-->>CLI: Updated resources
        CLI->>K8s: GET post-migration verification
        K8s-->>CLI: Verified state
        CLI-->>User: Migration report<br/>(steps completed, color-coded)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 249, 196)
        Note over User,TrustyAI: Flow 3: TrustyAI Metrics Backup
        User->>CLI: kubectl odh migrate run trustyai.metrics<br/>--namespace my-ns
        CLI->>K8s: GET TrustyAIService<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: TrustyAI instance
        CLI->>K8s: GET Route (TrustyAI)<br/>Discover service endpoint
        K8s-->>CLI: Route host URL
        CLI->>TrustyAI: GET /metrics/spd/requests<br/>GET /metrics/dir/requests<br/>GET /metrics/drift/meanshift/requests<br/>Auth: Bearer Token, TLS: InsecureSkipVerify
        TrustyAI-->>CLI: Scheduled metrics JSON
        CLI->>FS: Write metrics backup<br/>(JSON, file mode 0600)
        CLI-->>User: Backup complete<br/>(metrics count, file path)
    end

    rect rgb(232, 232, 232)
        Note over User,GH: Flow 4: Dependency Installation (deps)
        User->>CLI: kubectl odh deps --refresh
        CLI->>GH: GET values.yaml<br/>from odh-gitops repo (commit 1a55af0)
        GH-->>CLI: Dependency manifest YAML
        Note over CLI: Parse dependencies<br/>Validate catalog sources<br/>(redhat-operators, community-operators,<br/>certified-operators, redhat-marketplace)
        CLI->>K8s: GET existing Subscriptions<br/>Check installed state
        K8s-->>CLI: Current operator state
        CLI->>K8s: CREATE Subscription<br/>Approve InstallPlan
        K8s-->>CLI: Operator installed
        Note over CLI: Poll CSV until succeeded<br/>(with timeout)
        CLI-->>User: Dependencies installed
    end
